Add spooky charm to your new tab with Anime Girl Halloween! This Chrome extension brings Halloween spirit with a cute and mysterious anime girl.

The Anime Girl Halloween live wallpaper extension combines festive visuals with anime flair, creating a hauntingly beautiful backdrop for your browsing. Its sleek design complements essential tools, enhancing both style and function.

Browse seamlessly with the Google search bar, organize shortcuts to top sites, and stay updated with a clock-date display.

Key Features:

Live Wallpaper featuring a charming Halloween-themed anime girl
Google Search Bar for fast browsing
Customizable site shortcuts for quick access
Clock-Date display to keep track of time

Celebrate Halloween anime-style with Anime Girl Halloween! Explore Gameograf.com for more exciting themes.
